Rupee ee Pakistan (Urdu: Rabbiga / ALA-LC: Rūpiyah; saxiix: Nambarka: PKR) waa lacagta Pakistan. Bixinta lacagta ayaa waxaa maamula Bankiga Gobolka Pakistan, Bangiga Dhexe ee dalka. Calaamadda ugu badan ee loo isticmaalo rupee waa Rs, oo loo isticmaalo risiidhada markii la iibsanayo badeecadaha iyo adeegyada.
Pakistan, rupee ayaa sidoo kale lagu qeexay "rupees", "rupaya" ama "rupaye". Sida caadiga ah ee Ingiriisiga Pakistan, qiimaha ballaadhan ee rupees waxaa lagu tiriyaa kumanaan, lakh (100,000) iyo aduun (10 milyan), 1 Arab (1 bilyan), 1 Kharab (100 bilyan).
